- [military] King Derthert's dismissal of the 'Iron King' as mere superstition has been met with a calculated mobilization of House Molarn's levies. While Vlandian steel moves toward the cliffs of Cananc to strike at the sea raiders, a formal diplomatic overture has been extended to the Western Empire to secure trade routes. The atmosphere along the coast remains thick with tension as merchants wait to see if the 'legend' will be silenced or if the Western Empire will embrace Vlandia's hand in cooperation. (created 9 days ago)
