    - Sparta (id:town_ES4) - town, culture: Laconia, faction: Sparta (id:sparta). Notables: Phirentos the Cooper (id:CharacterObject_3719), Haratheos the Cargomaster (id:CharacterObject_3720), Ascyron the Clothier (id:CharacterObject_3721), Rhanos the Thorn (id:CharacterObject_3722), Sleepy Jespara (id:CharacterObject_3723)
